OL,3,CFirst Minister Vaughan Gething defends
OL,4,Ccuts to Wales' national museums
OL,6,FFirst Minister Vaughan Gething has
OL,7,Fdefended Welsh Government cuts to
OL,8,FWales' national museums amid worries
OL,9,Fits base in Cardiff could be forced to
OL,10,Fclose due to the condition of the
OL,11,Fbuilding.
OL,13,FAt his first press conference as first
OL,14,Fminister, Mr Gething said funding the
OL,15,FNHS is his government's main priority
OL,16,Fdespite Museum Wales saying it expects
OL,17,Fto axe 90 jobs after a cut in their
OL,18,Ffunding.
