OL,4,Ccuts to Wales' national museums
OL,6,FMr Gething told a press conference in
OL,7,FEbbw Vale: "Real choices have to be
OL,8,Fmade about what we're not going to do."
OL,10,FIt comes after Museum Wales chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Jane Richardson spoke with
OL,12,FBBC Radio Wales' Sunday Supplement
OL,13,Fprogramme, revealing the organisation
OL,14,Fis facing a #4.5million reduction in
OL,15,Fits budget, which is set by the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment, who themselves are cutting
OL,17,Fspending in most portfolios.
