OL,3,CFirst Minister Vaughan Gething defends
OL,4,Ccuts to Wales' national museums
OL,6,FHeledd Fychan MS, spokesperson for
OL,7,Fculture, said: "The Labour Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment just don't get culture.
OL,10,F"While they're happy to pose for a
OL,11,Fpicture outside one of Wales' national
OL,12,Fmuseums or benefit from invites to
OL,13,Fexhibits, the reality is that 25 years
OL,14,Fof Labour rule has seen our culture
OL,15,Fand heritage institutions cut to the
OL,16,Fbone.
OL,18,F"As a result, we're now seeing job
OL,19,Flosses, museums potentially closing,
OL,20,Fand national collections at risk.
